WARD FERRY is an independent investment firm founded in 2000 and based in Hong Kong. The firm manages investment funds focused on the Asia Pacific region for global institutional investors. Ward Ferry Management Limited is regulated by the Hong Kong Securities and Futures Commission and the United States Securities and Exchange Commission.








