China Lodging Group LTD (HTHT) Holder Ward Ferry Management LTD Lowered Its Stake


					

						July 27, 2017 - By Richard Conner

Ward Ferry Management Ltd decreased its stake in China Lodging Group Ltd (HTHT) by 22.15% based on its latest 2016Q4 regulatory filing with the SEC. Ward Ferry Management Ltd sold 496,291 shares as the company’s stock rose 35.67% with the market. The institutional investor held 1.74 million shares of the consumer services company at the end of 2016Q4, valued at $90.41 million, down from 2.24M at the end of the previous reported quarter. Ward Ferry Management Ltd who had been investing in China Lodging Group Ltd for a number of months, seems to be less bullish one the $6.69 billion market cap company. The stock rose 0.20% or $0.2 reaching $96.17. About 71,835 shares traded. China Lodging Group, Ltd (ADR) (NASDAQ:HTHT) has risen 127.67% since July 27, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 110.97% the S&P500.







More notable recent China Lodging Group, Ltd (ADR) (NASDAQ:HTHT) news were published by: Marketwatch.com which released: “95.67” on October 08, 2010, also Seekingalpha.com with their article: “Possible Jewel In The Chinese Hospitality Sector” published on December 15, 2015, Seekingalpha.com published: “A Safe Short For 2016” on February 13, 2016. More interesting news about China Lodging Group, Ltd (ADR) (NASDAQ:HTHT) were released by: Globenewswire.com and their article: “China Lodging Group, Limited Reports First Quarter of 2017 Results” published on May 10, 2017 as well as Benzinga.com‘s news article titled: “The Positive And Negative For China Lodging Group” with publication date: June 06, 2016.
China Lodging Group, Ltd (ADR) (NASDAQ:HTHT) Ratings Coverage
Among 7 analysts covering China Lodging (NASDAQ:HTHT), 6 have Buy rating, 0 Sell and 1 Hold. Therefore 86% are positive. China Lodging had 13 analyst reports since August 18, 2015 according to SRatingsIntel. The rating was downgraded by Zacks to “Hold” on Thursday, August 20. The rating was upgraded by Deutsche Bank on Friday, December 30 to “Buy”. The stock of China Lodging Group, Ltd (ADR) (NASDAQ:HTHT) has “Hold” rating given on Wednesday, November 11 by Deutsche Bank. The stock has “Neutral” rating by Credit Suisse on Wednesday, August 19. The firm has “Equal-Weight” rating given on Wednesday, August 17 by Morgan Stanley. The stock has “Buy” rating by Brean Capital on Wednesday, August 17. The stock of China Lodging Group, Ltd (ADR) (NASDAQ:HTHT) has “Buy” rating given on Monday, November 9 by TH Capital. The company was upgraded on Thursday, October 8 by Goldman Sachs. Credit Suisse initiated it with “Outperform” rating and $66 target in Friday, February 3 report. The rating was upgraded by Credit Suisse on Wednesday, October 14 to “Outperform”.


